initiative which he took on September 30, 1998, to ask his Deputy
Special Representative, Dame Ann Hercus, to begin a process of
on-island talks with both sides with a view to reducing tension
and promoting progress towards a just and lasting settlement.
</P>
<P>
Cyprus has been divided since 1974.  
