opportunities and challenges, adding that the multi-polarization
of the world and the globalization of the economy brings China
closer to the rest of the world.
</P>
<P>
Moreover, China's reform and opening-up is coming to a critical
period after 20 years since it was first introduced. Meanwhile,
the development of modern science and technology and the
knowledge-based economy will all offer China the most exciting
opportunities as well as risks, it emphasizes.
</P>
<P>
Experience in the past year proves that adherence to the basic
theory, line and programs of the Chinese Communist Party is
a prerequisite and decisive factor in overcoming difficulties and
becoming successful, the editorial says.
</P>
<P>
Finally, it calls on the people to hold higher the great banner
of Deng Xiaoping Theory, unite closer around the CPC Central
Committee with Jiang Zemin at the core, grasp the opportunities on
offer and work hard for further development. 
