franc will be dead on Friday. The stock exchange of Paris
formally abandoned the franc on Wednesday, without champagne.
When it resumes trade on Monday, the stocks will be listed in
euro. The exchange rates between European currencies and euro and
between the dollar and euro will be announced on Thursday in
Brussels by the finance ministers of Euroland countries.
</P>
