on the Afghan issue, official sources said Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Shamshad is scheduled to meet Iranian Foreign Minister Kamal
Kharazi and other senior Iranian officials on ways and means to
settle the long-running Afghan crisis, the sources said.
</P>
<P>
